headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Faded Dinka Tee for Collectors Only
content: All GTA Online players who previously picked up the Dinka Tee will receive a faded version — the Dinka Aged Tee — just for playing this week. Keep it neatly folded and maybe it could eventually sell for a tremendous amount to a tight-trousered hipster on an auction site in the distant future.
